line\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36593,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/06\/06\/obedience-usri-yusra\/","url_meta":{"origin":36596,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sultan: Obey authorities in prosperity and adversity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 6, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou must listen and obey authorities in hardship and ease, what you are eager for and what you dislike, even if they give undue preference over you.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1836 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2087,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/17\/no-obedience-creator\/","url_meta":{"origin":36596,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Obedience: No obeying creation if disobeying the Creator","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no obedience to anyone if it is disobedience to Allah. Verily, obedience is only in good conduct.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7257, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1840 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u064d\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/